FinBERT sentiment classification was implemented using the yiyanghkust/finbert-tone model provided through the Hugging Face Transformers library, based on the FinBERT architecture introduced by Yang et al. (2020).
Yang, Y., Zhang, Y., & Wang, D. (2020). FinBERT: A pre-trained language model for financial communications. arXiv:2006.08097.
